title: JetBrains PhpStorm 8.0.1
description:
PhpStorm 8 brings yet even more emerging technologies to help you enjoy web development with deepest ever code understanding and advanced support for remote environments.

Year / Release Date : 2014 
Version : 8.0.1 
Developer : JetBrains 
URL: https://www.jetbrains.com/idea/ 
Bit : 32bit, 64bit 
Language : English 

System requirements :
Microsoft Windows 8/7/Vista/2003/XP (incl. 64-bit)
1 GB RAM minimum
2 GB RAM recommended
1024x768 minimum screen resolution
